Start with PHPBB.

Here is a list of systems based on previous requests and top competition.
PHPBB (https://www.phpbb.com/)
Woltlabs Bulletin Board ($ https://www.woltlab.com/en/)
Xenforo ($ https://xenforo.com/)
Buddypress (https://buddypress.org/)
SMF (https://simplemachines.org/)
Vanilla (https://github.com/vanilla/vanilla)
Discourse (https://github.com/discourse/discourse - Ruby and Postgres)

We also get requests for Wordpress but this would import into Articles or Blogs and is a bit different.
Wordpress (https://wordpress.org/)

